{
  "info": {
    "name": "AllocateAI - Competitor Confirmation Flow",
    "description": "Complete flow for competitor confirmation including approval and dismissal paths.\n\nIMPORTANT: Frontend owns the competitor display and selection.\n\nFlow:\n1. Python stores competitor suggestions in competitorSnapshot after Stage 1\n2. Frontend reads competitorSnapshot directly from DB\n3. User reviews/edits competitors on frontend\n4. Frontend saves confirmed selection to confirmedCompetitors in DB\n5. Frontend calls POST /confirm endpoint\n6. Python reads confirmedCompetitors from DB and proceeds to Stage 2",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://127.0.0.1:8003",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "sessionToken",
      "value": "test-session-12345",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "runId",
      "value": "1",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "1. Approval Flow",
      "description": "Complete flow: Start → Wait for confirmation → (Frontend saves competitors) → Approve → Complete\n\nNOTE: Between steps 1.2 and 1.3, frontend must:\n1. Read competitorSnapshot from ProjectVersionAiRun in DB\n2. Display to user for review/selection\n3. Save confirmed selection to confirmedCompetitors in DB\n\nOnly then call the confirm endpoint.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "1.1 Start Run",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "X-Session-Token",
                "value": "{{sessionToken}}"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"run_id\": {{runId}},\n  \"action\": \"start\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/runs",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "runs"]
            },
            "description": "Start a new generation run. This triggers Stage 1 (competitor matching).\n\nAfter Stage 1 completes, competitor suggestions are stored in:\nProjectVersionAiRun.competitorSnapshot"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "1.2 Poll Status (until awaiting_confirmation)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "X-Session-Token",
                "value": "{{sessionToken}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/runs/{{runId}}/status",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "runs", "{{runId}}", "status"]
            },
            "description": "Poll until status = 'awaiting_confirmation'.\n\nExpected response:\n{\n  \"status\": \"awaiting_confirmation\",\n  \"progress\": \"Waiting for competitor confirmation...\"\n}\n\n--- FRONTEND ACTION REQUIRED ---\n\nOnce status is 'awaiting_confirmation', frontend must:\n\n1. READ from DB:\n   SELECT \"competitorSnapshot\" \n   FROM \"ProjectVersionAiRun\" \n   WHERE \"externalRunId\" = {{runId}}\n\n2. Display competitors to user for review/selection\n\n3. WRITE to DB (user's confirmed selection):\n   UPDATE \"ProjectVersionAiRun\"\n   SET \"confirmedCompetitors\" = ARRAY['Brand1', 'Brand2', ...]\n   WHERE \"externalRunId\" = {{runId}}\n\n4. Then call the confirm endpoint (step 1.3)"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "1.3 Confirm Competitors (Approved)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "X-Session-Token",
                "value": "{{sessionToken}}"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"run_id\": {{runId}},\n  \"action\": \"approved\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/runs/{{runId}}/competitors/confirm",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "runs", "{{runId}}", "competitors", "confirm"]
            },
            "description": "Signal approval to proceed with Stage 2-4.\n\nPREREQUISITE: Frontend must have saved confirmedCompetitors to DB before calling this endpoint.\n\nRequest body:\n- action: \"approved\" - Proceed with Stage 2\n- action: \"dismissed\" - Cancel the run\n\nThis endpoint:\n1. Reads confirmedCompetitors from DB (set by frontend)\n2. If empty/null, returns 400 error\n3. If valid, triggers Stage 2-4 pipeline\n\nResponse includes the confirmed_competitors list that will be used."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "1.4 Poll Status (until completed)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "X-Session-Token",
                "value": "{{sessionToken}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/runs/{{runId}}/status",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "runs", "{{runId}}", "status"]
            },
            "description": "Poll until status = 'completed'.\n\nStatus progression after confirmation:\n- generating (S2) → parsing (S3) → completing (S4) → completed"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "1.5 Get Allocation Result",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "X-Session-Token",
                "value": "{{sessionToken}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/runs/{{runId}}/result",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "runs", "{{runId}}", "result"]
            },
            "description": "Get the final allocation result.\n\nReturns:\n- allocations: Array of channel allocations with share_pct, budget, reasoning\n- total_budget_eur: Total budget\n- kpi_projection: Projected KPI impact\n- reasoning_summary: Overall strategy summary"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "1.6 Download Debug ZIP",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "X-Session-Token",
                "value": "{{sessionToken}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/runs/{{runId}}/debug-zip",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "runs", "{{runId}}", "debug-zip"]
            },
            "description": "Download debug ZIP file containing all pipeline data.\n\nUse 'Send and Download' in Postman to save the ZIP file.\n\nContents:\n- S2_prompt.txt: Full prompt sent to GPT-4\n- S2_llm_response.txt: Raw LLM response\n- S2_parsed_raw.json: Parsed JSON before post-processing\n- S2_final_result.json: Final allocation result\n- Y1/Y2/Y3 files: YouGov data pipeline\n- N1 file: Nielsen brand matching\n- FINAL_filtered_data.json: Combined data for LLM"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "2. Dismissal Flow",
      "description": "Flow: Start → Wait for confirmation → Dismiss → Cancelled\n\nDismissal does NOT require frontend to save confirmedCompetitors first.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "2.1 Start Run",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "X-Session-Token",
                "value": "{{sessionToken}}"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"run_id\": {{runId}},\n  \"action\": \"start\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/runs",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "runs"]
            },
            "description": "Start a new generation run for dismissal test."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "2.2 Poll Status (until awaiting_confirmation)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "X-Session-Token",
                "value": "{{sessionToken}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/runs/{{runId}}/status",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "runs", "{{runId}}", "status"]
            },
            "description": "Poll until status = 'awaiting_confirmation'."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "2.3 Dismiss Competitors",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "X-Session-Token",
                "value": "{{sessionToken}}"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"run_id\": {{runId}},\n  \"action\": \"dismissed\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/runs/{{runId}}/competitors/confirm",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "runs", "{{runId}}", "competitors", "confirm"]
            },
            "description": "Dismiss the competitor set and cancel the run.\n\nNo need to save confirmedCompetitors for dismissal.\n\nResponse:\n{\n  \"status\": \"cancelled\",\n  \"message\": \"Run cancelled\"\n}"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "2.4 Verify Cancelled Status",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "X-Session-Token",
                "value": "{{sessionToken}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/runs/{{runId}}/status",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "runs", "{{runId}}", "status"]
            },
            "description": "Verify status is 'cancelled'.\n\nExpected:\n{\n  \"status\": \"cancelled\",\n  \"progress\": \"Cancelled\"\n}"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "3. Error Cases",
      "description": "Test error handling",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "3.1 Confirm Without Saving Competitors",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "X-Session-Token",
                "value": "{{sessionToken}}"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"run_id\": {{runId}},\n  \"action\": \"approved\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/runs/{{runId}}/competitors/confirm",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "runs", "{{runId}}", "competitors", "confirm"]
            },
            "description": "Try to confirm without frontend saving confirmedCompetitors first.\n\nExpected: 400 Bad Request\n{\n  \"detail\": \"No confirmed competitors found. Frontend must save competitor selection to confirmedCompetitors before calling confirm.\"\n}"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "3.2 Confirm on Non-Awaiting Run",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "X-Session-Token",
                "value": "{{sessionToken}}"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"run_id\": {{runId}},\n  \"action\": \"approved\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/runs/{{runId}}/competitors/confirm",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "runs", "{{runId}}", "competitors", "confirm"]
            },
            "description": "Try to confirm a run that is not in 'awaiting_confirmation' status.\n\nExpected: 400 Bad Request\n{\n  \"detail\": \"Run is not awaiting confirmation. Current status: completed\"\n}"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "3.3 Mismatched Run ID",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "X-Session-Token",
                "value": "{{sessionToken}}"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"run_id\": 999,\n  \"action\": \"approved\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/runs/{{runId}}/competitors/confirm",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "runs", "{{runId}}", "competitors", "confirm"]
            },
            "description": "Run ID in body doesn't match URL.\n\nExpected: 400 Bad Request\n{\n  \"detail\": \"run_id in body (999) does not match URL (1)\"\n}"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "3.4 Invalid Action",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "X-Session-Token",
                "value": "{{sessionToken}}"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"run_id\": {{runId}},\n  \"action\": \"invalid\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/runs/{{runId}}/competitors/confirm",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "runs", "{{runId}}", "competitors", "confirm"]
            },
            "description": "Invalid action value.\n\nExpected: 422 Validation Error\nAction must be 'approved' or 'dismissed'"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
